column4: Conditional Admit is specified as the category under which an applicant has been granted an official offer to enroll in a postsecondary institution.

Other Admit is specified as the category under which an applicant has been granted an official offer to enroll in a postsecondary institution.
Then applicant has NOT been granted an official offer to enroll in the postsecondary institution.
